codePut:
UPDATE SFRENSP SET SFRENSP_ESTS_CODE = 'ES'
WHERE SFRENSP_TERM_CODE=:SFRENSP_TERM_CODE
AND SFRENSP_PIDM=:parm_user_pidm
AND SFRENSP_KEY_SEQNO=:SFRENSP_KEY_SEQNO
codeGet:
SELECT SFRENSP_TERM_CODE as ID, SFRENSP_TERM_CODE ,SFRENSP_KEY_SEQNO FROM SFRENSP
WHERE SFRENSP_PIDM=:parm_user_pidm
AND SFRENSP_KEY_SEQNO=:p_seq_no
